1. How to compile and install:

You need:
    o  autoconf 2.60
    o  automake 1.9 (tested with 1.9.6)
    o  libtool 1.5 (tested with 1.5.24)

Type the following sequence of commands:

 autoreconf -vif
 ./configure
 make
 make install


2. Examples

After exmpp installation, you can compile the examples in the examples directory with the command:

erlc *.erl
